	<div class="wrapper">
		<section class="columns">
			<div class="column">
				<h2>Our Story</h2>
				<p class="statements">We set out to make a change in the way we approach our health. We believe that in order to change our health habits, there needs to be a platform that is both fun, easy to use, and rewarding. What better way than combining the fun and excitement of social media, with resources that ensure a much more fulfilling experience with your health, mentally and physically.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="column">
				<h2>Our Mission</h2>
				<p class="statements">Create a fun and supportive community of people centered around health.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="column">
				<h2>Our Values</h2>
				<p class="statements"><strong>Passion:</strong> We believe that the best products are built from teams who have an unwavering passion to change industry standards.</p>
				<p class="statements"><strong>Integrity:</strong> We hold ourselves to the highest level of integrity in everything we do.</p>
				<p class="statements"><strong>Customer obsession:</strong> We put our focus into aligning our products with what our consumers want.</p>
			</div>
		</section>
	</div>
</main>

